July 28, 2017 7:55 PM ET
Insurance

Company Overview of Global Atlantic Financial Group Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Global Atlantic Financial Group Limited, through its subsidiaries, operates as a financial services company that provides retirement and protection products, as well as reinsurance solutions. The company offers life insurance products, such as term life, universal life, and indexed universal life that help meet the retirement and protection needs, as well as reinsurance solutions protection, wealth transfer, and small-business needs of customers in the United States. It also provides products for capital, risk, and business solutions for insurance companies; property and casualty insurance products; release capital/improve return on equity, risk management, exit non-core businesses, acquisit...
Global Atlantic Financial Group Limited, through its subsidiaries, operates as a financial services company that provides retirement and protection products, as well as reinsurance solutions. The company offers life insurance products, such as term life, universal life, and indexed universal life that help meet the retirement and protection needs, as well as reinsurance solutions protection, wealth transfer, and small-business needs of customers in the United States. It also provides products for capital, risk, and business solutions for insurance companies; property and casualty insurance products; release capital/improve return on equity, risk management, exit non-core businesses, acquisition financing, and new business reinsurance; and variable, fixed index, and fixed annuities for retirement investors. In addition, the company specializes in reinsurance, restructuring, and acquisitions of businesses to help institutions achieve their strategic objectives. Global Atlantic Financial Group Limited was formerly known as Goldman Sachs Reinsurance Group and changed its name to Global Atlantic Financial Group Limited. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda with offices worldwide.
Detailed Description


