**** PRENEED AND IMO ANNUITY AGENT IMPORTANT NOTICE****
If you are licensed to sell our products as either a preneed life insurance agent or an IMO annuity agent, please review the following message to avoid any delays in processing your business.
To comply with federal law, Global Atlantic requires all licensed agents to complete AML training and certify compliance every two years on a rolling 24 month basis. If you are a licensed agent, you must have a current Anti-Money Laundering (“AML”) training certificate on file to continue writing with us.
If you have not completed your AML training and certification within the past 24 months, you are required to do so. Agents who submit business after May 1, 2017, and have not completed the appropriate training and certification, will be asked to do so prior to new business being issued. Please complete these requirements as soon as possible. We do not want any delays in processing your business.
For additional information, e-mail Licensing@gafg.com
 



                      Attn: IMO Annuity Agents Effective 7/10/17, in order to access our new administrative platform, please register your new agent ID. This agent ID will begin with Mxxxxxxxx.

SECURITY UPDATE 
In order to tackle the latest online threats, we are updating our agent portal security. As a result, the next time you log in you may be asked to change your password. If you use multiple member IDs, you will need to complete this action for each of your credentials.
Final Expense agents will need to call (888) 606-6372 in order to obtain access to your account.












