Keep a promise. Even after you’re gone.





At Global Atlantic, we help you plan ahead. We want to protect the same thing you do: your loved ones. You promise to help them, and we promise to help you with our suite of life insurance products offering  both:
A range of traditional life insurance options
Funeral and memorial planning
 

 Traditional Life Insurance


Life insurance is about life, your life. It's about how you want to live your life right now and 20 years from now. It's also about how your loved ones will live their lives when you're gone. At Global Atlantic, we want to help you find a plan that fits your needs. With a focus on indexed universal life insurance, we offer a suite of options to help meet the protection, wealth transfer and small-business needs of customers throughout the United States.
Explore Indexed Universal Life
 
Explore Universal Life
 
Explore Term Life
 




Funeral and Memorial Planning


A funeral and memorial plan will help make your wishes known, so your loved ones won’t have to worry or second guess if they made the right choice. There are several ways to make sure your funeral or memorial service is funded, so you can help relieve your family from future financial responsibility. Of all the things you can do for your family, planning and funding your funeral may be the most considerate and caring.
 



 







 









